{"tid":2344763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【周梓樂死因研訊】專家證人：難以排除自行去矮牆並誤會後有行人道 暫未有資料支持被襲假設","createTime":"2020-12-29T04:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T05:20:34.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c81eb1ee828e5f801660a3879fec0d279e865625","tid":2344763,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:14:17.000Z","msg":"周梓樂死因研訊 難以排除自行去矮牆並誤會後有行人道<br />\n<br />\n科大學生周梓樂死因研訊繼續。專家證人表示，根據調查，難以排除周梓樂自行走去矮牆，並誤會矮牆後面有行人道，導致今次事件。<br />\n<br />\n他又指出，若有人要襲擊周梓樂並避開閉路電視鏡頭的可能性很微，暫時沒有片段或資料支持相關假設。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567606-20201229.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567606-20201229.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx4aGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=4b909c56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567606-20201229.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=24255a2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567606-20201229.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"920fdbd88ad620aab82b7fc537a14782d1a60c95","tid":2344763,"uid":292024,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:25:47.000Z","msg":"反手後面俾人推段片點計？"},{"pid":"0009907b2736144e9870b830404f7e26109234c2","tid":2344763,"uid":328494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c81eb1ee828e5f801660a3879fec0d279e865625","tid":2344763,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:14:17.000Z","msg":"周梓樂死因研訊 難以排除自行去矮牆並誤會後有行人道<br />\n<br />\n科大學生周梓樂死因研訊繼續。專家證人表示，根據調查，難以排除周梓樂自行走去矮牆，並誤會矮牆後面有行人道，導致今次事件。<br />\n<br />\n他又指出，若有人要襲擊周梓樂並避開閉路電視鏡頭的可能性很微，暫時沒有片段或資料支持相關假設。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567606-20201229.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567606-20201229.h